    'name' => 'weather_alerts',
    'description' => 'Fetch active weather alerts, warnings, watches, and advisories from the US National Weather Service API (free, no key required). Supports lookup by US state code or NWS zone ID. Returns structured alert data: event type, headline, severity, urgency, affected areas, effective/expires times, description, and safety instructions. First weather alert/warning capability in the ecosystem — completely new domain from weather_forecast. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
